{
  "stem": "10162.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I never, ever, ever thought of going to any organization.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It just didn't even occur to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I got a-- first, I, I, I entered-- I heard that, if you were a student.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because this was a young, a very young immigration after the-- after the revolution.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "These were mostly students and young people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So that if you're a student, you can go and enter any French university, and you will get a stipend or a scholarship.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I wasn't a student anymore, but I dec-- I could be because I was still in my 20s, and they said, if you're under 30.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so I, I went to they called the Ecole des Beaux-Arts-- the Academie des Beaux-Arts-- fine arts academy.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had to take a-- an ex-- an entry-- entrance exam, which I passed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I got a scholarship.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and, and I took advantage of all this incredible things that France offers to its citizens and, and-- not citizens, inhabitants-- ever since the French Revolution.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I lived in-- I lived-- of course, I didn't have to pay tuition.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got a scholarship.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got a place to live in Cit-- Cite Universitaire, and I could eat there at, at their cafeteria.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I still had plenty of time left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I would-- I was accepted to the last year to the-- of the-- of the academy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was an [INAUDIBLE] class, so it was OK if I just went once or twice a week.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had a full-time job, at least one, if not two, all the time, also.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was working for a perfume house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I learned the French perfume business inside-out, which was good because that's how I got to America.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
